ent/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/acshadows-kujikiri-yamashiro.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/acshadows-kujikiri-yamashiro.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/acshadows-kujikiri-yamashiro.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/acshadows-kujikiri-yamashiro.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/acshadows-kujikiri-yamashiro.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Ubisoft Quebec/Ubisoft via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe region north of Izumi Settsu, Yamashiro, has \u003cstrong\u003ethree Kuji-kiri locations\u003c/strong\u003e. Luckily, they’re all fairly close to synchronization points, making them easier to reach via fast travel. Situated on a mountain, the Kuji-kiri west of Shoryuji is the trickiest to reach, but there’s a road you can follow from the castle. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"omi-kuji-kiri-locations\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOmi Kuji-Kiri locations\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/acshadows-kujikiri-omi.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1080\" data-pswp-width=\"1920\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A map shows all Omi kuji-kiri locations in AC Shadows\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" lo