ins-creed-shadows-guides/542428/companions-allies-how-to-recruit-all-list\"\u003ecompanions\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/assassins-creed-shadows-guides/542414/romance-options-all-list-how-to-unlock\"\u003eromance options\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
